statements: SELECT property_id, owner_id, owner_name, property_address, ownership_start_date, ownership_end_date FROM property_ownership_records;
SELECT owner_name, property_id, property_address FROM property_ownership_records WHERE ownership_start_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM property_ownership_records WHERE owner_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT owner_name, property_address FROM property_ownership_records WHERE ownership_end_date IS NULL;
SELECT property_id, owner_id, property_address FROM property_ownership_records ORDER BY ownership_start_date DESC, property_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM property_ownership_records WHERE owner_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT property_id, owner_name, property_address FROM property_ownership_records WHERE ownership_start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT owner_name, property_id, property_address, ownership_start_date FROM property_ownership_records WHERE ownership_end_date IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM property_ownership_records WHERE property_address LIKE '%Ave%' ORDER BY ownership_start_date DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT owner_name FROM property_ownership_records WHERE ownership_start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND ownership_end_date IS NULL ORDER BY owner_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM property_ownerships WHERE owner_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT owner_name, ownership_start_date FROM property_ownerships WHERE ownership_end_date IS NULL;
SELECT property_id, owner_id, ownership_start_date, ownership_end_date FROM property_ownerships WHERE ownership_end_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT transaction_id, property_id, seller_id, buyer_id, transaction_date FROM property_transactions WHERE buyer_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM property_transactions WHERE transaction_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM property_ownerships WHERE owner_id = '1e17a13d-1564-4a89-87c6-0419c5a528d0' ORDER BY ownership_start_date DESC;
SELECT owner_name, ownership_start_date, ownership_end_date FROM property_ownerships WHERE ownership_end_date IS NULL;
SELECT property_id, owner_name FROM property_ownerships JOIN property_transactions ON property_ownerships.property_id = property_transactions.property_id;
SELECT DISTINCT owner_id, COUNT(*) AS property_count FROM property_ownerships GROUP BY owner_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;

SELECT owner_id, owner_name, COUNT(*) AS total_transactions FROM property_ownerships JOIN property_transactions ON property_ownerships.property_id = property_transactions.property_id GROUP BY owner_id;
SELECT * FROM Properties;
SELECT property_address, owner_name FROM Properties WHERE property_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT owner_name, contact_number FROM Owners WHERE email_address = 'example@email.com';
SELECT * FROM PropertyOwnership WHERE ownership_start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_address, owner_name, contact_number FROM Properties p JOIN PropertyOwnership po ON p.property_id = po.property_id JOIN Owners o ON po.owner_id = o.owner_id;
SELECT * FROM Properties WHERE property_id = '12345';
SELECT owner_name, property_address FROM Properties WHERE owner_name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM Owners JOIN PropertyOwnership ON Owners.owner_id = PropertyOwnership.owner_id WHERE PropertyOwnership.ownership_start_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT owner_name, email_address FROM Owners JOIN PropertyOwnership ON Owners.owner_id = PropertyOwnership.owner_id WHERE PropertyOwnership.ownership_end_date IS NULL;
SELECT property_address, contact_number FROM Properties JOIN Owners ON Properties.owner_name = Owners.owner_name;
SELECT * FROM property_owners ORDER BY owner_id DESC;
SELECT owner_name, ownership_percentage FROM property_owners WHERE property_id = 2;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_properties FROM properties;
SELECT property_address, property_value FROM properties WHERE property_value > 500000 ORDER BY property_value ASC;
SELECT transaction_id, transaction_date FROM transactions WHERE transaction_amount < 1000 ORDER BY transaction_amount DESC;
SELECT owner_id, owner_name, property_id, ownership_percentage FROM property_owners WHERE owner_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM properties WHERE property_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT audit_id, transaction_id, audit_timestamp FROM audit_trail WHERE transaction_id = 1 ORDER BY audit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_address, property_value FROM properties WHERE property_value > 100000 ORDER BY property_value DESC;

SELECT owner_name, property_address, transaction_amount FROM property_owners INNER JOIN properties ON property_owners.property_id = properties.property_id INNER JOIN transactions ON property_owners.property_id = transactions.property_id WHERE transaction_amount > 50000 ORDER BY transaction_amount DESC;
SELECT * FROM PropertyOwners;
SELECT OwnerName, OwnerAddress FROM PropertyOwners WHERE OwnerID = 1;
SELECT PropertyAddress, PropertyValue FROM Properties WHERE PropertyValue > 500000;
SELECT TransactionID, TransactionDate FROM OwnershipHistory ORDER BY TransactionDate DESC;
SELECT DocumentType, DocumentLink FROM PropertyDocuments WHERE PropertyID = 3;
SELECT OwnerName, OwnerAddress FROM PropertyOwners;
SELECT PropertyAddress, PropertyValue FROM Properties ORDER BY PropertyValue DESC;

SELECT OwnerName, PropertyAddress, DocumentType FROM PropertyOwners JOIN OwnershipHistory ON PropertyOwners.OwnerID = OwnershipHistory.OwnerID JOIN Properties ON OwnershipHistory.PropertyID = Properties.PropertyID JOIN PropertyDocuments ON Properties.PropertyID = PropertyDocuments.PropertyID;

SELECT DISTINCT OwnerName, PropertyAddress, TransactionDate FROM PropertyOwners JOIN OwnershipHistory ON PropertyOwners.OwnerID = OwnershipHistory.OwnerID JOIN Properties ON OwnershipHistory.PropertyID = Properties.PropertyID JOIN PropertyTransactions ON OwnershipHistory.TransactionID = PropertyTransactions.TransactionID ORDER BY TransactionDate ASC;

SELECT OwnerName, PropertyValue AS 'Value of Property', TransactionAmount AS 'Transaction Amount' FROM PropertyOwners JOIN OwnershipHistory ON PropertyOwners.OwnerID = OwnershipHistory.OwnerID JOIN Properties ON OwnershipHistory.PropertyID = Properties.PropertyID JOIN PropertyTransactions ON OwnershipHistory.TransactionID = PropertyTransactions.TransactionID WHERE TransactionAmount > 10000;
